    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>IMPORTANT: </strong>Does not support Mac right now.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>THIS IS A DEMO</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the role of the Vipunk, also known as the shield of Valhalla. It is your job to destroy and fight back against the invading robots sent from the future. Vipunk is a bullet-hell survivor game with a focus on deflecting enemies' attacks. Adapt, evolve, and overcome to drive back the robots!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Try your best:</strong> In this demo, you will be able to play on the island map with a boss at the end. Try and see if you can beat it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chest arena:</strong> Every time you level up, a chest will spawn on the map, creating an arena. If you win the arena battle, you will be rewarded with cards. You can level up  5 times.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329390/extras/e6821e7a1c03028955a1c5a5f0192586.poster.avif?t=1732136534\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329390/extras/e6821e7a1c03028955a1c5a5f0192586.webm?t=1732136534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329390/extras/e6821e7a1c03028955a1c5a5f0192586.mp4?t=1732136534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique fighting style: </strong>In VIPUNK you never shoot any bullets yourself. Using the Shield of Valhalla you use their own weapons against them by parrying their bullets back at them</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329390/extras/dc85a50dbe0065a02b7972cfc49270e4.poster.avif?t=1732136534\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329390/extras/dc85a50dbe0065a02b7972cfc49270e4.webm?t=1732136534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329390/extras/dc85a50dbe0065a02b7972cfc49270e4.mp4?t=1732136534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Getting stronger:</strong> Each run is different, in VIPUNK you have access to powerup cards, these cards will help you get stronger,  Experiment with 10 different cards.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329390/extras/852673a9234de49d441f3c9577263c68.poster.avif?t=1732136534\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329390/extras/852673a9234de49d441f3c9577263c68.webm?t=1732136534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329390/extras/852673a9234de49d441f3c9577263c68.mp4?t=1732136534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenge the boss:</strong> Fight the skeleton head boss, who is part of the robot lords and defeat him! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329390/extras/dd58d94e25a30567ef5582afc9fded45.poster.avif?t=1732136534\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329390/extras/dd58d94e25a30567ef5582afc9fded45.webm?t=1732136534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329390/extras/dd58d94e25a30567ef5582afc9fded45.mp4?t=1732136534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
